# Credentials and secrets — defense in depth, the platform's threat
# model assumes uploaded bot images carry no per-user secrets but a
# leaked dotfile in a contributor's working tree is still bad.
*.key
*.pem
*.cert
*.crt
secrets.*
credentials.*
.aws/credentials

# Build artifacts
*.tar.gz
*.zip
*.whl
